===Etymology 2===
{{zh-forms}}
After singer {{w|Cai Xukun}} ({{lw|zh|蔡徐坤}}), based on a [[mondegreen]] of the lyrics {{m|zh||只因你太美|tr=zhǐ yīn nǐ tài měi|t=just because you are too pretty}} in his song {{lw|zh|只因你太美}} with the boy group {{lw|zh|SWIN-S}}, misheard as {{m|zh||雞你太美|tr=jī nǐ tài měi|t=chicken, you are too pretty}}.

The sense of "two and a half years" was quoted from his introduction at ''{{w|Idol Producer}}'' in 2015.

